== PyXDG ==

PyXDG is a python library to access freedesktop.org standards. Currently supported are:

 * Base Directory Specification Version 0.6
 * Menu Specification Version 1.0
 * Desktop Entry Specification Version 1.0
 * Icon Theme Specification Version 0.8
 * Recent File Spec 0.2
 * Shared-MIME-Database Specification 0.13

[[http://pyxdg.readthedocs.org/en/latest/index.html|Documentation on ReadTheDocs]]

=== Development ===

Development takes place in [[http://cgit.freedesktop.org/xdg/pyxdg/|a git repository]], with a [[https://github.com/takluyver/pyxdg|Github mirror]]. Freedesktop.org hosts the [[https://bugs.freedesktop.org/buglist.cgi?product=PyXDG&component=PyXDG&resolution=---&list_id=97030|bug tracker]].

[[http://travis-ci.org/#!/takluyver/pyxdg|{{https://secure.travis-ci.org/takluyver/pyxdg.png?branch=master}}]]

